Montego Bay International is located in Montego Bay, Jamaica.
It was origionally created by OleRae in 2021
It was one of the few tracks when revamping I had access to the old model so the layout has the exact same dimensions.
In revamping the northern walls were brought closer to the track, and a section was added off to the northwest, so the track could act as the beginning/end of a rally stage.
Almost all the decoration except for the stands on the start/finish line were added by me.
